#: app/templates/landing.html:586
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "Kun maal dha?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:588
msgid ""
"The Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) helps teams add local knowledge to "
"map features\n"
"        by coordinating mapping in the field."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) gareewwan beekumsa naannoo amala kaartaa"
" irratti dabaluu keessatti isaan gargaara, hojii kaartaa dirree "
"qindeessuudhaan."

#: app/templates/landing.html:592
msgid ""
"Field-TM facilitates collaborative mapping by supporting and extending "
"mature tools\n"
"        like ODK and QField. It is a standalone mobile and web workflow "
"that helps teams collect\n"
"        geospatial data efficiently with commonly available Android "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"Field-TM meeshaalee cimoo akka ODK fi QField deeggaruun fi babal'isuun "
"kaartaa waliinii ni mijeessa. Inni adeemsa hojii moobaayilaa fi weebii of"
" danda'e kan gareewwan meeshaalee Android yeroo baay'ee argaman "
"fayyadamuun data geospatial gahumsaan walitti qabuu gargaaru dha."

#: app/templates/landing.html:599
msgid "A project manager demonstrates FieldTM mapping workflow on a laptop"
msgstr ""
"Hogganaan pirojektii tokko adeemsa hojii kaartaa FieldTM laptop irratti "
"agarsiisaa jira"

#: app/templates/landing.html:605
msgid "Main Features"
msgstr "Amaloota ijoo"

#: app/templates/landing.html:608
msgid "Flexible Data Collection"
msgstr "Walitti qabuu dataa laafaa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:610
msgid ""
"Support diverse survey forms, multiple data formats, and adaptable "
"workflows that\n"
"          fit different operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Foormii qorannoo garaagaraa, foormaata dataa hedduu, fi adeemsa hojii "
"fedhii hojiirra oolmaa garaagaraa waliin wal madaalu ni deeggara."

#: app/templates/landing.html:615
msgid "Open Source and Customizable"
msgstr "Madda banaa fi haala barbaadamuun jijjiiramuu danda'u"

#: app/templates/landing.html:617
msgid ""
"Adapt Field-TM to your own survey logic, data structures, and integration"
"\n"
"          requirements."
msgstr ""
"Field-TM mantii qorannoo, caasaa dataa, fi fedhii walitti hidhaminsa kee "
"waliin madaqsi."

#: app/templates/landing.html:622
msgid "Entity-Level Tracking"
msgstr "Hordoffii sadarkaa wantaa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:624
msgid ""
"Monitor survey progress at task and feature level so managers can make "
"informed\n"
"          decisions quickly."
msgstr ""
"Hoggantoonni murtoo odeeffannoo qabu saffisaan akka kennanitti guddina "
"qorannoo sadarkaa hojii fi amalaatti hordofi."

#: app/templates/landing.html:632
msgid "Who is it for?"
msgstr "Eenyuf dha?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:635
msgid "Project Manager"
msgstr "Hogganaa pirojektii"

#: app/templates/landing.html:636
msgid "Create and coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Duula dirree uumii qindeessi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:638
msgid ""
"Project managers use Field-TM to set up mapping projects, define areas of"
" interest,\n"
"          design survey forms, and split work into manageable tasks."
msgstr ""
"Hoggantoonni pirojektii Field-TM pirojektoota kaartaa qopheessuuf, "
"naannoo fedhii ibsuuf, foormii qorannoo qopheessuuf, fi hojii gara hojii "
"bulchuu danda'amutti qooduuf fayyadamu."

#: app/templates/landing.html:642
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
msgstr "Naannoo pirojektii ibsi fi foormii qorannoo olkaa'i ykn filadhu"

#: app/templates/landing.html:643
msgid "Split the area into tasks and generate a data extract"
msgstr "Naannoo sana gara hojiiwwanitti qoodi fi baafata dataa uumi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:644
msgid "Publish the project to ODK Central or QFieldCloud"
msgstr "Pirojektii gara ODK Central ykn QFieldCloud maxxansi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:645
msgid "Share a QR code so mappers can start collecting data"
msgstr "Kaarta hojjettoonni data walitti qabu jalqabuuf koodii QR qoodi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:649
msgid "Field Mapper"
msgstr "Kaarta hojjataa dirree"

#: app/templates/landing.html:650
msgid "Collect data in the field with your phone"
msgstr "Bilbila kee fayyadamuun dirree keessatti data walitti qabi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:652
msgid ""
"Mappers do not need to log in to Field-TM. Once a project manager "
"publishes a\n"
"          project, mappers access it directly in their mobile app of "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Kaarta hojjettoonni gara Field-TM seenuu hin qaban. Hogganaan pirojektii "
"pirojektii tokko maxxanse erga, kaarta hojjettoonni appii moobaayilaa "
"filatan keessatti kallattiin argatu."

#: app/templates/landing.html:656
msgid "Scan the QR code shared by your project manager"
msgstr "Koodii QR hogganaan pirojektii kee qoodde skaan godhi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:657
msgid "The project loads automatically in ODK Collect or QField"
msgstr "Pirojektiin ofumaan ODK Collect ykn QField keessatti fe'ama"

#: app/templates/landing.html:658
msgid "Navigate to your assigned task area and collect data"
msgstr "Gara naannoo hojii siif ramadamee deemi, dataas walitti qabi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:659
msgid "Submit your survey, which goes straight to the server"
msgstr "Qorannoo kee ergi; inni kallattiin gara seervaraatti deema"

#: app/templates/landing.html:666
msgid "Field-TM Use Cases"
msgstr "Fayyadama Field-TM"

#: app/templates/landing.html:671
msgid "Field mapping in progress"
msgstr "Kaartaan dirree adeemsarra jira"

#: app/templates/landing.html:676
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Kaartaa hawaasaa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:678
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public\n"
"            facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager hawaasa qubannaa al-idilee, tajaajila uummataa, fi "
"tajaajiloota naannoo kaartessuuf humneessa, karoora hirmaachisaa ta'eef."

#: app/templates/landing.html:683
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Karooraa fi bulchiinsa magaalaa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:685
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities\n"
"            through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Gandoota, daandiiwwan, fi bu'uura tajaajilaa qorannoo qindaa'e fi hojii "
"kaartaa ifa ta'een bulchuu danda'amuun magaalaa ogeessa ta'e ijaari."

#: app/templates/landing.html:690
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Deebii balaa fi haaromsa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:692
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate "
"volunteers, and\n"
"            deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Balaa booda bu'uura tajaajilaa miidhame saffisaan kaartessi, fedhii tola "
"ooltota qindeessi, hojii gargaarsaaf data amanamaa dhiheessi."

#: app/templates/landing.html:701
